metadata.name: Animyst DAO Membership
metadata.description: Animyst DAO Membership is key to unlocking DAO membership benefits, governance privileges, and lifetime access to the Animyst DAO ecosystem. It allows holders to participate in governance decisions, earn $GEMZ staking rewards, and become an integral part of the DAO. Your VIP Membership NFT entitles you to an airdrop of 3,000 $GEMZ during the presale on Arbitrum. It is also a rare and exclusive collectible that represents early support and contribution to the Animyst DAO community and ecosystem. Animyst DAO is a community-owned lifestyle ecosystem that empowers users to elevate their journey with luxury travel, premium cannabis, and accessible DeFi opportunities. The DAO is committed to community ownership and decentralization through participation in the decision-making processes and shaping the direction of the entire ecosystem through $GEMZ governance. The DAO is dedicated to cultivating connections and facilitating access to both DeFi & IRL opportunities that unlock new business prospects, inspire fresh ideas, and foster professional relationships with prominent and influential figures in the Ethereum and Arbitrum DeFi communities.
